	* cvshowto.txt: new file, taken from d1x webpage
	* AUTHORS, README: Taking over as maintainer of d2x
	* ChangeLog: Grab mouse with SDL/X11
	* main/: gamecntl.c, inferno.c: Grab mouse with SDL/X11

